com.github.dm.jrt.android.proxy.v11.core

Class JRoutineProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.proxy.core.JRoutineProxy
      • com.github.dm.jrt.android.proxy.core.JRoutineProxy
        • com.github.dm.jrt.android.proxy.v11.core.JRoutineProxy

  • public class JRoutineProxy
extends JRoutineProxy
    Utility class used to create builders of objects wrapping target ones, so to enable asynchronous calls of their methods, bound to a context lifecycle.

    The builders returned by this class are based on compile time code generation, enabled by pre-processing of Java annotations.
    The pre-processing is automatically triggered just by including the artifact of this class module.

    See JRoutineProxyCompat for support of API levels less than 11.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 05/06/2015.

    See Also:
    Android Annotations, LoaderProxy, Annotations
